title: Discovering a beloved Victorian bay
caption: Discovering a beloved Victorian bay
desc: Welcome to Whisky Bay, a summer gem for Victorians. Visit at just the right time of day and you’ll see many of the Bay’s rocks enveloped in warm sunlight - presenting colours not too dissimilar from a fine glass of whisky. But this is just one of many incredible spots to visit within Wilsons Promontory National Park, or ‘The Prom’ as it’s more commonly known by locals.
